appointments

Class AppointmentScheduling

  • java.lang.Object
    • appointments.AppointmentScheduling

  • public class AppointmentScheduling
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages appointment scheduling, including viewing, rescheduling, and scheduling new appointments. It handles available slots, doctor availability, and appointment booking.
